{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act33side", "eventName": "巴別塔", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BB-10", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "再見，再見", "storyInfo": "特蕾西婭在生命的最後時刻，決定抹除博士的記憶，並在博士漫無邊際的記憶中見到了那個意想不到的人。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ghosthunter_intro", "key": "$ghosthunter_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g10_theresaoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭很慶倖阿米婭睡著了。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭沒有看見博士的背叛，也沒有看見特蕾西婭最後的悲傷。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在特蕾西婭將議長室中的最後一名刺客抹除的同時，那頂黑色的王冠終於安穩地傳遞到了阿米婭的手中。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#9$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事了，阿米婭，沒事了……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#9$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經結束了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#9$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沒有看向那個已經僵直在原地的人，只是輕輕拍了拍懷中孩子的後背，在那張稚嫩的小臉上，落下一吻。"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭。我沒辦法放棄億萬生命和萬年時間才換來的機會。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒辦法允許你們突破源石的規劃。沒辦法允許你……將這片大地變成一個美好但短暫的夢。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你傷害了阿米婭。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#4$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……既然魔王已看過了我的記憶，那我們多說無益。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你恨我嗎？", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你傷害了阿米婭，你也即將傷害凱爾希，和那些信任你的將士。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#4$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你對待如今這些生命的方式嗎？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#5$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會盡全力保證他們不在接下來的衝突中喪命。這也是特雷西斯給我的承諾。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要……你的死亡。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……博士，你是出於此刻的愧疚而來到我面前的嗎？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起我所做的事情，愧疚的份量……太輕。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在凱爾希都不熟知的年代裡，我們做出了太多選擇。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是……", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等阿米婭長大後，若她還記得我，若她問起我，你是否會如實告知她……我是怎樣離去？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#10$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會幫助他們尋找另一種生活。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尋找在源石毀滅泰拉之前最後的安穩？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#10$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……抱歉。這無法改變。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你明知道這無法改變……你卻仍舊，想治好阿米婭的病。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕在不遠的未來，阿米婭的家人、家鄉，和你們未來可能建立起聯繫的那些人和事，都將成為不變的源石。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也不忍看著眼前的孩子受苦。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你的真心。是你的純潔。是你的本性。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我其實……很欣慰，博士。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#9$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很高興，凱爾希願意相信的那個你，願意相信我們的那個你，是真實存在的。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#9$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……源石的締造者……{@nickname}。你是毀去一切的毒，也可以是一切的解藥。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……什麼？", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothtrailground", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看見特蕾西婭強撐著站起，將雙手伸向自己，博士本能地想要後退。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士卻發現自己的身體無法移動分毫，博士發現自己的悲傷遠勝自己強撐的理性。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只好任由特蕾西婭觸碰面罩之下的面龐。"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在落淚，博士……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，你就是這樣的人。你明知道自身的脆弱，明知道哪怕是此時的我，也對你有致命的威脅……你還是來了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我還是……願意相信你。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信原本的你。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信那個，將雨露和豔陽帶給我們的{@nickname}。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_1", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_5", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.5, "fillto": 0.15, "fadetime": 0.01}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.5, "fillto": 0.15, "fadetime": 0.01}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g10_theresaoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 100.0, "duration": 60.0, "ease": "OutQuad", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.8, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-200,-380", "posto": "-100,-380", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 60.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "49_g10_theresaoffice", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一張臉，既熟悉又陌生。特蕾西婭清楚它的樣子。"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她從未有機會如此直觀地從上面捕捉到情緒。"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她微笑著伸出手指，眼前的景象猶如布匹一般被撕裂開。"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨後，她緩緩抽出自裂口處鬆脫的絲線，殘餘的畫面也散解開來，博士的記憶不斷消散。"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magicwarmthy", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "wa"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "wa", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭頭也不回地繼續深入，繼續將每一寸組成博士靈魂的記憶都拆解為一團團蒼白混亂的斷線。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像是很久很久之前的夜晚，幼小的她在特雷西斯身旁自學縫紉那般。"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記憶消散殆盡，靈魂只剩下了最後一枚碎片。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而記憶的盡頭處有一個背影。特蕾西婭對那個背影熟悉而又陌生。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是博士，也不是博士。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.4}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.15, "fillto": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.15, "fillto": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_white", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<color=#000000>你在對我做什麼，特蕾西婭？</color>", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_light", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.8, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,-380", "posto": "100,-380", "duration": 60.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然已經是最後了，但我突然想賣個關子，你可不要怪我啊，博士。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會對你說……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“去找到你自己吧。”", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "wa", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}